snippet.title: Play Tennis Official Trailer
snippet.description:
From the makers of Tank hero, Tank hero:Laser Wars, and Sector Strike comes Play Tennis.

 Fast paced table tennis action comes to your Android device. Perform smashing serves and side-spin shots to take out your opponents in the most exciting sports simulation on your mobile phone.

Android Market link: http://j.mp/tankheroandroid

This is the official trailer for Play Tennis, the hit tennis game available for Android
